* arith_loop.sno
* Benchmark: pure arithmetic dispatch — tight counter loop, no I/O or patterns.
* 1,000,000 iterations.  Reports elapsed ms via TIME().
* Expected last line: 1000000
    &TRIM = 1
    &STLIMIT = 10000000
    T1 = TIME()
    N = 0
LOOP    N = N + 1
    N = LT(N, 1000000) N        :S(LOOP)
    T2 = TIME()
    OUTPUT = "iterations: " N
    OUTPUT = "ms: " (T2 - T1)
END
